      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IM FRANKEE (8) hasn't raced here since she made a winning debut over this distance in April and has been good since, finishing second in both a heat and the final of the Nutrien Classic Sales 2F Series Final at Wagga. Draws wide but had enough speed to lead from a similar barrier last time. Big chance. SAN ANTONIO (3) looks close to a win after back-to-back placings. Beaten only 1.4m here two back before a third at Listed level in the Nutrien Classic Sales 2CG Series Final. Should get his chance from this draw. CHIEF KENNY (2) was runner-up for the third time in four starts at this circuit and distance when 6m away last time. Draws for another good showing. MAJARO GIRL (7) draws wide but came from a similar barrier to place last start and beat SAN ANTONIO for a win at this circuit and distance two back.",
